Articles.Content:
I have a problem with quickload (or loading a past save in general). It seems to work, I press f5 and it says "quicksaving", I hold f9 and it says "hold f9 to load a quicksave". But after holding f9, il lags for a pair of second, and nothing happends, the rocket just flies like i didn't do anything. The weird thing is that when I go to the main menu i can't load if I tried to load a save, and I have to exit the game and enter again. I can't do it manualy neither. I tried uninstalling and reinstalling the game, I deleted cache, I've been looking for some answer in the forums... but nothing seems to solve it. It started when I cheated A 600 parts craft to orbit. If you have any slution, please make me know.
And yes, the quicksave option is enabled, my pc runs on windows 10 64bits, and I deleted the 600 parts caft.
(BTW sorry about my bad english)
